[[伽利略定位系统|伽利略定位系统]]是由操作欧洲导航卫星系统管理局(GNSS)和[[欧洲空间局|欧洲空间局]]和附近实现全面运行覆盖全球。伽利略于2016年12月15日开始提供全球早期作战能力（EOC），提供第三套，也是第一套非军用的全球导航卫星系统，当时计划在2019年达到完全作战能力（FOC）。<ref name="operational">{{cite web|url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Navigation/Galileo_begins_serving_the_globe|title=Galileo begins serving the globe|publisher=European Space Agency|access-date=2016-12-15|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913073120/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Navigation/Galileo_begins_serving_the_globe|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="European Commission"/>为了实现伽利略的FOC覆盖星座目标，需要添加计划中的额外卫星。伽利略系统时间（GST）是一个连续的时间标度，它是由地面站意大利富奇诺伽利略控制中心生成的精确定时设施，它基于不同原子钟的平均值，并由伽利略中央部分维护，并与TAI，标称偏移低于50[[纳秒|纳秒]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gsc-europa.eu/system/files/galileo_documents/OS_SIS_OSD_Web.pdf |title=European GNSS (Galileo) Open Service Signal-In-Space Operational Status Definition, Issue 1.0, September 2015 |access-date=2020-10-25 |archive-date=2017-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109163657/https://www.gsc-europa.eu/system/files/galileo_documents/OS_SIS_OSD_Web.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.unoosa.org/pdf/icg/2009/icg-4/45d.pdf |title=1 The Definition and Implementation of Galileo System Time (GST). ICG-4 WG-D on GNSS time scales. Jérôme Delporte. CNES – French Space Agency. |access-date=2020-10-25 |archive-date=2016-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161106184619/http://www.unoosa.org/pdf/icg/2009/icg-4/45d.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Galileo’s clocks">{{cite web|url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Navigation/Galileo/Galileo_s_clocks|title=Galileo's clocks|publisher=European Space Agency|access-date=2017-01-16|archive-date=2019-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829183314/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Navigation/Galileo/Galileo_s_clocks|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="European Commission">{{cite news|title=Galileo's contribution to the MEOSAR system|url=http://ec.europa.eu/growth/sectors/space/galileo/sar/meosar-contribution/index_en.htm|accessdate=2015-12-30|publisher=European Commission|archive-date=2016-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160709033428/http://ec.europa.eu/growth/sectors/space/galileo/sar/meosar-contribution/index_en.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 根据GNSS机构的说法，伽利略提供30[[纳秒|纳秒]]的定时精度。<ref name="Timing accuracy">{{cite web|url=https://www.gsa.europa.eu/galileo/services/initial-services|title=GALILEO GOES LIVE|publisher=European GNSS Agency|date=2016-12-15|access-date=2017-02-01|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115130957/http://www.gsa.europa.eu/galileo/services/initial-services|dead-url=no}}</ref> 欧洲GNSS服务中心于2018年3月发布的季度绩效报告指出，UTC时间传播服务精度为≤7.6[[纳秒|纳秒]]，这是通过在过去12个月中累计样本并超过≤30[[纳秒|纳秒]]的目标得出的。<ref name="Timing accuracy2">{{cite web|url=https://www.gsc-europa.eu/system/files/galileo_documents/Galileo-IS-OS-Quarterly-Performance_Report-Q4-2017.pdf|title=GALILEO INITIAL SERVICES – OPEN SERVICE – QUARTERLY PERFORMANCE REPORT OCT-NOV-DEC 2017|publisher=European GNSS Service Centre|date=2018-03-28|access-date=2017-03-28|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826181137/https://www.gsc-europa.eu/system/files/galileo_documents/Galileo-IS-OS-Quarterly-Performance_Report-Q4-2017.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gsc-europa.eu/electronic-library/performance-reports |title=Galileo Open Service and Search and Rescue - Quarterly Performance Reports, containing measured performance statistics |access-date=2020-10-25 |archive-date=2019-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826170704/https://www.gsc-europa.eu/electronic-library/performance-reports |dead-url=yes }}</ref>每个伽利略卫星都有两个被动式氢[[微波激射器|微波激射器]]和两个[[铷|铷]][[原子钟|原子钟]]，用于机载计时。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spectratime.com/products/ispace/passive-maser/|title=Passive Hydrogen Maser (PHM)|website=spectratime.com|access-date=2020-10-25|archive-date=2019-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/w